ss=\"int-value\">Adjudication Decision</span><span><span class=\"crit-badge crit-async\">informational</span></span></div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:6px;\"><span class=\"int-label\">Relationship:</span> <span style=\"font-size:13px;\">produces</span></div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:4px;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;\">Produces adjudication decisions</div>\n      \n    </div><div class=\"int-point\">\n      <div class=\"int-header\"><span class=\"int-value\">Claim Record</span><span><span class=\"crit-badge crit-async\">informational</span></span></div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:6px;\"><span class=\"int-label\">Relationship:</span> <span style=\"font-size:13px;\">uses</span></div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:4px;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;\">Uses claim records</div>\n      \n    </div><div class=\"int-point\">\n      <div class=\"int-header\"><span class=\"int-value\">Policy Reference</span><span><span class=\"crit-badge crit-async\">informational</span></span></div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:6px;\"><span class=\"int-label\">Relationship:</span> <span style=\"font-size:13px;\">uses</span></div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:4px;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;\">References policy data</div>\n      \n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2>Inbound Integration Points (5)</h2><div class=\"section\">\n    <div class=\"int-point\">\n      <div class=\"int-header\"><span class=\"int-value\">Claims Processing System</span><span><span class=\"crit-badge crit-async\">informational</span></span></div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:6px;\"><span class=\"int-label\">Relationship:</span> <span style=\"font-size:13px;\">container_of</span></div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:4px;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;\">Contains</div>\n    </div><div class=\"int-point\">\n      <div class=\"int-header\"><span class=\"int-value\">Claims Web UI</span><span><span class=\"proto-badge\">REST/HTTPS</span><span class=\"crit-badge crit-sync\">synchronous-critical</span></span></div>\n   